    <briefdescription>
<para>Class for making mesh from regular distance map. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>distance for each lattice of map is defined as point on ray from surface point cloud to direction point cloud, with length equal to 1/distance from distances file (if distance in file == 0 ray had no point) </para>
